<PageLayout
  title="Bremelanotide (PT-141): from a tanning peptide's side effect to an approved desire drug"
  kicker="Explainer"
  description="PT-141 began as an offshoot of the tanning peptide Melanotan II, when its trials produced an unexpected effect. Here's how it works on the brain rather than the bloodstream, what's actually approved, and how that differs from the grey-market 'PT-141' sold online."
